Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:15.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}妖灵会馆?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:16.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}您知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不过不知道这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}会馆素来低调
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果没有特地了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知道分馆也很正常。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:27.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是给您的卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:29.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是老君给您的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:30.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}给我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:31.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}有助您的恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:35.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}用完后再来这里还给你么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:36.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:39.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}您可以在一个可观的数额内随意消费
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊?老君对你说了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:45.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这卡也是各大会馆通用的通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:48.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是来这里的任何妖精都能获取的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}谁都能拿?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}看来您不是很了解现在的会馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:54.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}需要我为您讲解一下么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:55.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}方便么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:57.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}当然，这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}妖灵会馆由包括老君在内的三位神所创立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}分布在各大人类城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:05.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}专门为妖精提供服务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}除了自古就有的客栈作用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}现在还无偿提供在人类世界生存资金
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:12.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}什么都不用做?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:13.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不过需要遵守会馆法则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:17.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}会馆法则?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:19.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不得杀害同类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不得在人类面前暴露自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:24.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}如果愿意接受会馆召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:27.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}还可以获得更多的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:56.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}艾玛呀比划半天了到底打不打了还！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}唉，打呀……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我不说不说了行不不说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:08.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那是会馆的练武场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是刚才那群人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们也是这里的常客了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:14.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}因为外形原因无法住在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:16.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他们很强么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那怎么还没修炼成人形呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}每个妖精都有自己的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}人形与修为无关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}仅仅是因为方便融入人类而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}就算做不到也可以去找人形师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们只是不屑于变成人类而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们和馆长比谁强呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我应该是这里最弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那你怎么当上馆长的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:40.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我会赚钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}怎么赚钱呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}卖这里的树
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:47.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这里的树都是因为你而茂盛起来的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}啊，谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:50.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}和木系攻击型的速生速死不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我所催生的植物是自然生长的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:57.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}它们会继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}树那么值钱么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}一棵好树是非常值钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}特别是在这个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}赚钱就可以当馆长么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我们继续上楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}唔?这里不是顶楼了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:18.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}站稳咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里就是会馆的核心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}各地会馆的分布与信息都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}好壮观呐……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}一些流量大的会馆更壮观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}空间波动…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这里应该不只是放地图吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}图上的每个圆点代表着一个分馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}但不仅仅是代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}而是真正连接着两馆之间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你是说这些全都是空间点?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这个真的很棒呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}千针先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:00.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哟，馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}领新人参观呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:03.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}他们已经等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那再会了小妖精们~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}他们几个约在这里见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}他不讨厌人类么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他分辨不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是开放使用的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那不会有人捣乱么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}已经很久没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:25.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你们可以先看我们会馆的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}顶上的圆代表了这个会馆的主要属性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们是金色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就是以经商为主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}下面的点是常驻妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里包括我和秃贝在内一共三人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}但每个会馆都有很多人类在辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不经商的会馆怎么回应那些资助要求呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}会馆资源是共享的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}资金、空间、武力、法宝、灵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}馆长可以在权限范围内任意取用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}既然馆里也有人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:57.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}为什么还规定不能对人类暴露身份呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}其实知道我们存在的人也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}就像被玄离大人信任的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}但不是所有人都能接受我们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}以前还好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}但人类变得越来越强大之后就有点麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}经过几次事件之后我们才定下现在的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是现在最好的相处方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不是很懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}对了你们为什么要赚钱呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不能变出金子和钱什么的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那会破坏人类自身的金融结构
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:29.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}长远来看最好的办法就是按人类的规则赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这样看来我只能开冰库了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我只能偷东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这个不算赚钱啊喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}可以用这个传送发快递嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:38.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不好么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}基础介绍就是这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知您对高权限内容可有兴趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}暂时不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那我们去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}真的不吃个饭再走么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不了，爷爷还在家等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}今天真是麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}您客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这是给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}给我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不要拒绝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这个是老君给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你不是要帮他带周边么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}喔噢~~~~嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我现在送你去山新家么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们约好明天一起去看展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那我就先回村里修祠堂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}后天晚上来接你对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:39.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:41.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}山新呐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你怎么知道我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是啊我正要去你家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:47.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}外面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哥哥好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你怎么在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我来接小白呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}还要帮皇受接小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我还是回村里吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}府先生他们离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}往市里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们知道分寸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}好像在跟踪玄离大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们知道分寸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:26.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}下车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你也不想我们对车子出手吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:50.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知有何贵干?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}切磋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}为什么现在过来?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}有情况就有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}会被发现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:07:59.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:01.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}说路过他们会信么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你们怎么在这?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们是来帮您的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}不可能信吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:18.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}并没有
